description:
The UK’s most watchable label, O___o? chase aces by Dawuna, LA Timpa, Ize and Skins with another striking debut, introducing the rawly sophisticated R&B of Yorkshire/London’s Halina - RIYL Tirzah & Mica, Leila, Klein, baby_asl

By this point trust should be implicit with O___o? recruits, and clearly so with ‘The Game’; Halina’s bloozy rumination on “alienation, love and loss, adulation and anxiety” set to her tenderly tattered, bittersweet co-production with Saint Jude. Stemming from... more
